---
---
<section class="section-pad" style="padding-top: calc(var(--space-xl) * 1.2); padding-bottom: var(--space-xl); min-height: 85vh; display: flex; align-items: center;">
  
  <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: var(--space-xl); align-items: center;">
    
    <!-- LEFT: Copy Context -->
    <div style="max-width: 600px;">
      <div style="display: inline-block; padding: 0.5rem 1rem; background: var(--color-secondary); color: var(--color-accent); border-radius: 9999px; font-size: var(--text-sm); font-weight: 700; border: 1px solid var(--color-border); margin-bottom: var(--space-md);">
        Hands-Off Growth Systems
      </div>
      
      <h1 style="font-size: var(--text-5xl); margin-bottom: var(--space-sm); line-height: 1.1;">
        We build sales systems for <br/><span class="text-accent">design agencies.</span>
      </h1>
      
      <p style="font-size: var(--text-xl); color: var(--color-text-main); font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: var(--space-md);">
        Automate your sales and marketing processes for effortless execution.
      </p>

      <p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-lg); font-size: var(--text-lg);">
        The process of hiring in-house can be slow, expensive, and often results in a lack of expertise in creating optimal systems from the beginning. By partnering with us, you gain access to a team of award-winning automation experts ready to deploy enterprise-grade infrastructure.
      </p>

      <div style="display: flex; gap: var(--space-md); align-items: center;">
        <a href="https://calendly.com/andrickjohn-l0n9/30min" target="_blank" class="btn" style="padding: 1.25rem 2.5rem; font-size: var(--text-lg);">
          Let's Chat
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" style="margin-left: 0.5rem;"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path></svg>
        </a>
        <a href="#casestudies" style="color: var(--color-text-muted); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;">View Case Studies &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- RIGHT: Generated SaaS UI Mockup -->
    <div style="position: relative;">
      <div style="position: absolute; inset: -20px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.1), transparent); border-radius: 20px; filter: blur(20px); z-index: 0;"></div>
      <img src="/saas_dashboard.png" alt="SaaS Analytics Dashboard Mockup" style="width: 100%; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); position: relative; z-index: 1;" />
    </div>

  </div>

  <style>
    @media (min-width: 1024px) {
      .section-pad > div {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>

</section>
